title: Altass
text: Altass () is a village in the Parish of <a href="Creich">Creich</a>, near <a href="Lairg">Lairg</a>, <a href="Sutherland">Sutherland</a>, within the <a href="Scottish%20Highlands">Highland</a>, <a href="Scotland">Scotland</a> and is in the <a href="County%20council">council</a> area of <a href="Highland%20%28council%20area%29">Highland</a>.
